org.hypergraphdb.query.impl

Class TraversalResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hypergraphdb.query.impl.TraversalResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<Pair<HGHandle,HGHandle>>, HGSearchResult<Pair<HGHandle,HGHandle>>, TwoWayIterator<Pair<HGHandle,HGHandle>>, CloseMe

    public class TraversalResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements HGSearchResult<Pair<HGHandle,HGHandle>>

    TraversalResult wraps a graph HGTraversal as a query HGSearchResult. Because graph traversals are not bidirectional, this implementation will throw an UnsupportedOperationException from the backwards moving methods.
